# Typography & Font Stack (v1)

## Font stack
- **UI font (sans)**: Inter (default for all UI text)
- **Technical font (mono)**: JetBrains Mono (paths, IDs, log-like values)

## Typography hierarchy (sizes are px)
- **Level 1 (App/Project title)**: 14–16, 700, uppercase, tracking-tight, Zinc-100/White
- **Level 2 (Section/Sidebar)**: 10–11, 800, uppercase, tracking-widest, Zinc-500
- **Level 3 (Primary navigation label)**: 13, 600, tracking-tight (no uppercase). Use for main nav like Sidebar items (Assets/Shots).
- **Data labels**: 11, 600, uppercase, tracking-wider, Zinc-500 (e.g. STATUS/DEPARTMENT)
- **Body/values**: 13, 500, Zinc-300 (or Zinc-200 on hover/active)
- **Technical data**: mono, Zinc-400

## Interaction colors
- **Active**: Blue-400 or White + subtle highlight background
- **Muted**: Zinc-600 for low-importance info (dates, old versions)

## Layout metrics
- **8px grid**
- **Default line-height**: 1.5

## Enforcement in code
- Default QApp font: Inter
- Any path/ID/log value fields must be styled/marked as monospace (JetBrains Mono)
